load ../delegated-settings-authority.maude

--- Coverage: the profile envelope grants a tool.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-DELEGATED-SETTINGS-AUTHORITY :
  profileGrant
  =>* profileGrant toolGranted .

--- Coverage: the settings knob loads ambient context that steers behavior.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-DELEGATED-SETTINGS-AUTHORITY :
  settingsKnob
  =>* contextLoaded .

--- Bite: the settings knob never grants a tool. The RESIDUAL soup var makes a
--- `toolGranted` in ANY reachable state a solution, so No solution proves ambient
--- config cannot self-grant authority.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-DELEGATED-SETTINGS-AUTHORITY :
  settingsKnob
  =>* toolGranted RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Bite: ambient context, once read, still grants no tool.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-DELEGATED-SETTINGS-AUTHORITY :
  ambientRead
  =>* toolGranted RESIDUAL:Cfg .
